<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:15:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>焦点：挑战中国国酒对于西方白酒制造商来说是一项艰巨的任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/challenging-chinas-national-drink-is-tall-order-western-liquor-makers-2024-03-06/</link><description>寻求利用中国年轻饮酒者对威士忌和干邑白兰地日益增长的需求的全球饮料巨头在与中国主导白酒生产商的竞争中面临着挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/challenging-chinas-national-drink-is-tall-order-western-liquor-makers-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧元重返全球央行舞台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-is-back-scene-global-central-banks-2024-03-06/</link><description>曾经遭受危机和通货紧缩伤害的欧元，由于正利率回归和地缘政治对美元吸引力的挑战而受到央行储备经理的欢迎。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:03:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-is-back-scene-global-central-banks-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国在南海“故意挑起事端”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-deliberately-stirring-up-trouble-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>菲律宾周三指责中国在南海“故意挑起事端”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-deliberately-stirring-up-trouble-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，由于工厂陷入困境，中国一月至二月出口可能放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-jan-feb-factories-struggle-2024-03-06/</link><description>路透周三的一项调查显示，中国一月至二月的出口增长可能放缓，这表明制造商仍在为海外买家而苦苦挣扎，并需要国内进一步的政策支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-jan-feb-factories-struggle-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚对南海破坏稳定的行为表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-concerned-about-destabilising-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>周三，中国和菲律宾船只在争议海域发生冲突的第二天，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞表示，澳大利亚非常担心南海的不安全和破坏稳定的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-concerned-about-destabilising-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>瓦努阿图警方在美国海岸警卫队的协助下称中国船只违反了捕鱼法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vanuatu-police-aided-by-us-coast-guard-say-chinese-vessels-violated-fishing-laws-2024-03-06/</link><description>瓦努阿图警方和官员表示，当地警方对六艘中国渔船进行检查后，发现六艘中国渔船违反了瓦努阿图的渔业法。这些渔船是第一艘在瓦努阿图海域巡逻的美国海岸警卫队船只。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vanuatu-police-aided-by-us-coast-guard-say-chinese-vessels-violated-fishing-laws-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>病毒爆发后中国禁止从格鲁吉亚进口绵羊和山羊</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-bans-imports-sheep-goats-georgia-after-virus-outbreak-2024-03-06/</link><description>3月2日，海关总署发布公告称，因格鲁吉亚爆发绵羊、山羊痘疫情，中国暂停从格鲁吉亚进口绵羊、山羊及其相关产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-bans-imports-sheep-goats-georgia-after-virus-outbreak-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者涌向海外 境外投资触及上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-abroad-hitting-outbound-investment-limit-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国资金正以极快的速度涌入投资离岸资产的基金，这与境外投资限制相抵触，并使北京方面振兴国内市场和稳定人民币的努力变得更加复杂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:51:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-abroad-hitting-outbound-investment-limit-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在巴西建设生产基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-starts-construction-manufacturing-complex-brazil-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周三向路透社证实，该公司已开始在巴西建设生产基地。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-starts-construction-manufacturing-complex-brazil-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市引领亚洲走低，金价创历史新高后震荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-06/</link><description>亚洲股市周三在谨慎交易中走软，其中中国股市下滑，因为北京方面缺乏大规模刺激措施令一些投资者感到失望，而黄金和比特币在触及历史新高后有所回落。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪通过降低最便宜电动汽车的成本加深中国价格战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-lowers-starting-price-its-lowest-priced-ev-model-seagull-by-54-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪周三将其最便宜的电动汽车海鸥的价格下调了 5%，为中国残酷的价格战火上浇油。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-lowers-starting-price-its-lowest-priced-ev-model-seagull-by-54-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧佩克+减产压倒中国和美国需求担忧，油价反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-fell-slightly-china-growth-worries-clash-with-output-cuts-2024-03-06/</link><description>油价在延续下跌后于周三小幅反弹，原因是主要产油国减产带来的供应紧张迹象盖过了中国和美国这两个全球最大原油消费国的需求增长担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-fell-slightly-china-growth-worries-clash-with-output-cuts-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>南海紧张局势下东盟峰会聚焦海上安全和贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周三表示，随着北京寻求加强其在有争议的南中国海的存在，海上安全、贸易和清洁能源将塑造该国与东盟的未来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平召唤“新生产力”，但老问题依然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-summons-new-productive-forces-old-questions-linger-economy-2024-03-05/</link><description>面对多年来最严峻的经济挑战，中国领导层已责成各部委和地方政府落实习近平主席的新口号：释放“新生产力”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-summons-new-productive-forces-old-questions-linger-economy-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>参议员卢比奥寻求提高关税以阻止中国“涌入美国汽车市场”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senator-rubio-seeks-stiffer-tariff-stop-china-flooding-us-auto-markets-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国共和党参议员马可·卢比奥周二提议大幅提高中国汽车进口关税2万美元，以阻止中国“涌入美国汽车市场”，这是华盛顿保护美国汽车制造商和汽车工人的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senator-rubio-seeks-stiffer-tariff-stop-china-flooding-us-auto-markets-2024-03-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>